      <p class='static-card-content'> The list of Winners shall be posted on a separate web-page on the UCF.com. The winners will also be intimated by e-mail.In the event that a Participant has been declared a Winner on the abovementioned web-page but has not received any communication from UCF, such Participant may contact UCF within the time specified on the webpage.</p>
