      <p class='static-card-content'>  <b>Free Leauge</b>:  UCF is presenting an unbelievable offer in that users can win cash prize without paying any entry charges for the leagues and if you win! the winning amount will get transferred into your unutilized money which can be consumed only for joining other leagues. There is no other way to use or withdraw the winning amount accept joining other leagues. If it is found that a Participant playing the paid formats of the league(s) is under the age of eighteen (18), UCF shall be entitled, at its sole and absolute discretion, to disqualify such Participant and forfeit his/her prize. Further, UCF may, at its sole and absolute discretion, suspend or terminate such Participant’s account.To the extent permitted by law, UCF makes no representations or warranties as to the quality, suitability or merchantability of any prizes and shall not be liable in respect of the same. The Winners shall bear all transaction charges levied for delivery of cash prizes. All prizes are non-transferable and non-refundable. Prizes cannot be exchanged/redeemed for cash or kind. No cash claims can be made in lieu of prizes in kind.</p>
